Class StringUserTypeMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.amc.sakai.user.StringUserTypeMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserTypeMapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmptyStringUserTypeMapper

    public class StringUserTypeMapper
extends Object
implements UserTypeMapper
    Very simple UserTypeMapper which generates the same String value for any users. Technically, this object could be reconfigured at any time.
    Author:
    dmccallum
